summary: An ordinance accepting warranty deeds for portions of Lots 7 and 8, Block 20, Carleton Park Addition, as recorded in Volume 21 of King County Plats on Page 94, and Lots 1, 2, 3, 22, 23 and 24, Block 3, Minor's Addition to the City of Seattle, as recorded in Volume 2 of King County Plats at Page 12, for park, drive and boulevard purposes.
